There once was a village with a villager named Rob. Rob loved his village but when the werewolves attacked, they could never agree on who to lynch. Over time this slowly drove him mad. When the werewolves finally overran the village due to their indecisiveness, Rob managed to escape to another village, but he could never return to a normal life. His maddness even made him forget his own name. He called himself the "Zealot" and from that day on he decided he would take matters into his own hands when the villagers couldn't bring themselves to lynch someone. Unfortunately, he wasn't very good at spotting wolves and more often than not, he killed innocent villagers. They say Rob's spirit still haunts villages today, wolves and villagers fear him alike.
Zealot is a village role that kills a random person every night that there is no lynch (except n1). Kills pass through protection and can kill wolves or village roles
